@startuml sequence_chart
!theme plain
title Real-Time Line Chart Widget

actor User
participant "LineChartWidget" as W
participant "MetricsController" as C
participant "Handler" as H
database "DB" as DB
participant "RealtimeService" as RT
participant "TeamHub" as Hub

User -> W: mount widget
W -> C: GET /api/metrics/contactsCreatedDaily
C -> H: GetMetricQuery
H -> DB: SELECT date_trunc(day, CreatedAt), count(*) ...
H --> C: series
C --> W: 200
W --> User: render Chart.js

== domain change in another tab ==
note over Hub: contact created (slice 08 handler also publishes)
Hub --> RT: metricInvalidated:contactsCreatedDaily
RT --> W: notify
W -> C: GET /api/metrics/...
C --> W: refreshed series
W --> User: chart updates
@enduml
